- [GlycanBuilder2](https://github.com/glycoinfo/GlycanBuilder2) 1.25.0
- [WURCSFramework](https://gitlab.com/glycoinfo/wurcsframework) 1.2.14

- Parameters
- **format**: string (required) - Image format.
- `png`
- `svg`
- **type**: string (required) - Data type.
- `html`
- `json`
- `binary`
- **wurcs**: string (required) - WURCS format text.
- [Example](https://api.glycosmos.org/wurcs2image/1.25.0/png/html/WURCS%3D2.0%2F3%2C5%2C4%2F%5Ba2122h-1b_1-5_2%2ANCC%2F3%3DO%5D%5Ba1122h-1b_1-5%5D%5Ba1122h-1a_1-5%5D%2F1-1-2-3-3%2Fa4-b1_b4-c1_c3-d1_c6-e1)
- Response
- Body
![](data:image/png;base64,)

- Example

```
curl -d '{"format": "png", "type": "html", "wurcs": "WURCS=2.0/3,5,4/[a2122h-1b_1-5_2*NCC/3=O][a1122h-1b_1-5][a1122h-1a_1-5]/1-1-2-3-3/a4-b1_b4-c1_c3-d1_c6-e1"}' https://api.glycosmos.org/wurcs2image/1.25.0
```

Copy

- Request
- Body

```
{
"format": "png",
"type": "html",
"wurcs": "WURCS=2.0/3,5,4/[a2122h-1b_1-5_2*NCC/3=O][a1122h-1b_1-5][a1122h-1a_1-5]/1-1-2-3-3/a4-b1_b4-c1_c3-d1_c6-e1"
}
```
